node.text:
The 447 new cases of Covid-19 bring the the total number of infections in Singapore to 3,699.⁣
⁣
It is the highest single-day jump in infections here, the previous high being the 386 cases reported on Monday.⁣
⁣
#linkinbio to read more.⁣
